Participant's Agreement

By participating in this study, you acknowledge that:
 •	You have read the information provided in this consent form.
 •	You understand the purpose of the study, the procedures involved, and any potential risks.
 •	You voluntarily agree to participate in the research.

You understand that you can withdraw at any time without any consequences, and your data will be discarded.

Please click "I Agree" to indicate your consent to participate in this study. 
By clicking "I Agree", you are confirming that you have understood the information provided and agree to participate voluntarily.
